combined = phrases_ar |>
    group_by(article_id) |>
    summarize(total_phrases = sum(n)) |>
    inner_join(meta_ar, by = 'article_id') |>
    group_by(container.title, year) |>
    summarize(total_phrases = sum(total_phrases)) |> 
    collect()

ggplot(combined, 
       aes(year, total_phrases, 
               color = container.title, group = container.title)) +
    geom_line() +
    scale_y_log10()
